channel.title: setClientConfig list for 317
channel.description: Is there a list of all the setClientConfig ids for a 317 server? Like setClientConfig(166, 1); is dark brightness, setClientConfig(166, 2); is normal brightness, setClientConfig(166, 3); is bright brightness, and setClientConfig(166, 4); is very bright brightness. I need the setClientConfig codes for the running and walking button, but a whole list of them would be much better. Or if there's a way to look in the client itself to figure that out, that would help too.
